text: Daniela Rodrigues Da Silva (born 13 April 1999) is an Andorran footballer who plays as a defender. She has been a member of the Andorra women's national team. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers Category:Andorran people of Portuguese descent
